     <div type="preface">
   <head>The Preface.</head>
   <p>SEing that we haue already described the Disme, we will now come to the vse thereof, shewing by vi. Articles, how all computations which can hap<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>pen in any mans busines, may be easily performed thereby: beginning first to shew how they are to be put in practize, in the casting vp of the content or quantity of Land measured as followeth.</p>
